{"tid":1707890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵今日唔敢閂站 證明閒日抗爭同罷工係春袋","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T13:44:14.000Z","uid":63782,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"925c0d4faf04c977bbf47d4cf13a7e34c0800bb0","tid":1707890,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好再係閒日周圍塞同埋罷工 畢竟我係一隻好鍾意返工既港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8fb40dcac4d311c5a0b2e88f7389412a9fb135","tid":1707890,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！港版64早已發生<br />\n無謂再呃自己出面一切正常</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JiopVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JiopVK.jpg&h=8c9b5059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">之前山竹：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4ViaBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4ViaBR.jpg&h=c1033d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今日香港：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbH08nJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbH08nJ.png&h=acf9baee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhRdJV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh